      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nHi Lee,\n\nI did an experiment on onyx-26:\n\n [root@onyx-26 tests]# head ./maloo_upload.sh\n #!/bin/sh\n \n FILENAME=$1\n \n if [ -r ~/.maloorc ] ; then\n         source ~/.maloorc\n else\n         echo \"Error: ~/.maloorc not found.\" \\\n              \"Please obtain this file from the maloo web interface,\" \\\n              \"under 'Upload results'\"\n\n [root@onyx-26 tests]# ./maloo_upload.sh\n Error: ~/.maloorc not found. Please obtain this file from the maloo web interface, under 'Upload results'\n\nThe spaces were added automatically.",
